owl Dance&apos;s immediate burst damage, which would also encapture Malenia&apos;s character to boot (The excellent swordsman and the curse of her Scarlet Rot).<br/><br/>Instead of being a meme-y burst damage machine that randomly applies a status completely unconnected to Malenia (She doesn&apos;t bleed during her fight and nothing in her lore connects her to blood)</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16718510" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16718510" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">5</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>16</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>9</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16718510"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16718510" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16718510"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
